    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"#narrow/channel/287929-mathlib4/topic/Definition.20of.20ordinals/near/576329565\">A message</a> was moved here from <a class=\"stream-topic\" data-stream-id=\"287929\" href=\"/#narrow/channel/287929-mathlib4/topic/Unbundled.20relations.20and.20ordinal.20API/with/576193255\">#mathlib4 &gt; Unbundled relations and ordinal API</a> by <span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"459227\">Violeta Hern√°ndez</span>.</p>",
